description:
&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;lt;p&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;gt;This action gets the document from ServiceNow and attaches it to a record after signature status is signed.&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;lt;/p&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;gt;

&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;lt;p&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;gt;&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;lt;b&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;gt;Inputs:&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;lt;/b&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;gt;&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;lt;/p&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;gt;
&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;lt;ul&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;gt;	
	&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;lt;li&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;gt;&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;lt;b&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;gt;Envelope &amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;lt;/b&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;gt; - The envelope record that contains account, envelope id.&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;lt;/li&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;gt;
        &amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;lt;li&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;gt;&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;lt;b&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;gt;Target Record&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;lt;/b&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;gt; - The record to which the signed document will be attached.&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;lt;/li&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;gt;
        &amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;lt;li&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;gt;&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;lt;b&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;gt;Document Name&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;lt;/b&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;gt; - The name of the document which shall be used to attach the document to the record.&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;lt;/li&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;gt;
        &amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;lt;li&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;gt;&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;lt;b&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;gt;Document ID&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;lt;/b&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;gt; - The ID of the document which shall be attached to the record.&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;lt;/li&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;gt;
&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;lt;/ul&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;gt;

&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;lt;p&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;gt;&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;lt;b&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;gt;Outputs:&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;lt;/b&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;gt;&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;lt;/p&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;gt;
&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;lt;ul&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;gt;
	&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;lt;li&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;gt;&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;lt;b&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;gt;Status&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;lt;/b&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;gt; - Will be set to &amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;quot;Success&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;quot; if the request succeeds or &amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;quot;Error&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;quot; if a failure occurs.&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;lt;/li&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;gt;
	&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;lt;li&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;gt;&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;lt;b&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;gt;Error Message&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;lt;/b&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;gt; - Will be populated when the status is &amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;quot;Error&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;quot;.&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;lt;/li&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;gt;
        &amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;lt;li&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;gt;&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;lt;b&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;gt;Attachment&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;lt;/b&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;gt; - Reference record to that attachment that was created.&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;lt;/li&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;gt;
&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;lt;/ul&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;gt;

&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;lt;p&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;gt;&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;lt;b&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;gt;Error Messages:&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;lt;/b&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;gt;&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;lt;/p&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;gt;
&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;lt;ul&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;gt;
	&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;lt;li&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;gt;Provided Envelope ID or Document ID does not exist.&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;lt;/li&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;gt;
        &amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;lt;li&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;gt;Account ID is invalid or the associated credentials lacks sufficient permissions to access this resource.&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;lt;/li&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;gt;
	&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;lt;li&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;gt;The specified Integrator Key was not found or is disabled.Please verify the configured credential.&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;lt;/li&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;gt;
&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;lt;/ul&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;gt;

